## Events [/projects/{id}/events]
Provides a list of events for a single project.

### Retrieves an array of events [GET]

+ Parameters
  + id (string) ... The project ID.

+ Response 200

  + Body

            {
              "events": [
                {
                  "id": "60670752-25cd-426e-9faa-86a602ca4c90",
